---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import aboutImage from "@images/mobile-mechanic-roaters.jpg";
---

<section>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>About Our Mobile Mechanic services</h2>
        <div class="content">
            <p>
                At Wally’s Workshop, we believe that reliable, honest mechanical
                service should be easy to access, no matter where you are.
                That’s why Wally brings the workshop to you, offering fully
                mobile mechanic services across Glen Innes, Deepwater,
                Tenterfield, Inverell and nearby towns.
            </p>
            <Image
                src={aboutImage}
                alt="Mobile Mechanic Roaters Replacement"
                class="image"
            />
            <p>
                Wally is a licensed mechanic with years of hands-on experience
                working on everything from cars and bikes to trailers and farm
                equipment. Known for his no-fuss approach and quality
                workmanship, he takes pride in helping locals stay safe and
                moving without the stress of a traditional garage visit.
            </p>
            <p>
                Whether it's a logbook service, a breakdown on the roadside or
                general repairs at your property, Wally shows up on time, gets
                the job done right and keeps things simple. He’s not just
                servicing engines, he’s supporting the local community one job
                at a time.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    section {
        background-color: var(--bg-purple);
    }
    .container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
    }
    h2 {
        color: var(--text-purple);
        font-size: 2em;
    }
    .image {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        aspect-ratio: 1/1;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 16px;
    }
    .content {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        }
        .container {
            gap: 4rem;
        }
    }

    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
        .content {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1rem;
        }
        .container {
            gap: 6rem;
        }
        .image {
            width: 300px;
        }
        p {
            width: 80%;
        }
    }
</style>
